## Component Patterns

### Button — Primary


<button class="browse-btn" type="button">
  Label
</button>
```

- `background: rgb(0, 93, 171)`, `color: #fff`
- `border: 2px solid rgb(0, 93, 171)`, `border-radius: 3px`
- `padding: 8px 14px 8px 10px`, `font-size: 14px`, `font-weight: 700`
- `min-height: 40px`
- Hover: `background: rgb(0, 75, 140)`, `border-color: rgb(0, 75, 140)`

### Button — Ghost / Text

```
<button class="sign-in-btn" type="button">
  Label
</button>
```

- `background: none`, `border: none`
- `color: rgb(0, 93, 171)`, `font-size: 14px`, `min-height: 40px`
- Hover: `text-decoration: underline` or `color: rgb(0, 60, 120)`

### Button — Static CTA

```
<a class="static-button" href="...">Label</a>
```

- `background: rgb(0, 103, 184)`, `color: rgb(255, 255, 255)`
- `border: 2px solid transparent`, `border-radius: 2px`
- `padding: 10px 12px`, `font-weight: 600`, `line-height: 16px`

### Product Card

```
<article class="product-card">
  <a class="product-card-link" href="...">
    <div class="product-card-media">
      <img class="product-card-image" ... />
    </div>
    <div class="product-card-details">
      <h3 class="product-card-title">...</h3>
      <p class="product-card-description">...</p>
      <p class="product-card-price">...</p>
    </div>
  </a>
</article>
```

- Border: `1px solid var(--border)`, `border-radius: 12px`
- Background: `rgb(255, 255, 255)`, `box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)`
- Media: `aspect-ratio: 4/3`, `background: rgb(245, 245, 247)`
- Details padding: `16px`

### Static Content Card

```
<article class="static-card">
  <img class="static-card-image" ... />
  <div class="static-card-body">
    <h3 class="static-card-title">...</h3>
    <p class="static-card-text">...</p>
  </div>
  <div class="static-card-footer">
    <a class="static-text-link" href="...">CTA</a>
  </div>
</article>
```

- No border-radius, white background
- `box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.13) 0 3px 7px, rgba(0,0,0,0.11) 0 1px 2px`
- Body padding: `24px 24px 0`
- Footer padding: `16px 24px 24px`

### Eyebrow Text

```
<p class="featured-products-eyebrow">Label</p>
```

- `font-size: 14px`, `font-weight: 700`, `text-transform: uppercase`
- `letter-spacing: 0.56px`, `color: rgb(0, 93, 171)`

### Section Header

```
<div class="static-heading-block">
  <h2 class="static-section-title">Title</h2>
  <p class="static-section-description">Subtitle</p>
</div>
```

- Centered, `max-width: 66.6667%`, `margin: 0 auto 48px`

### Navigation Link

```
<a class="utility-link" href="...">Label</a>
```

- `color: rgb(0, 93, 171)`, `text-decoration: none`
- `font-size: 14px`, `padding: 2px 12px`
- Hover: `text-decoration: underline`

### Footer Links

```
<a class="footer-links-anchor" href="...">Label</a>
```

- `color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.72)`, `text-decoration: none`
- Hover: `text-decoration: underline`

## Layout

- **App container**: `max-width: 1126px`, centered, `border-inline: 1px solid var(--border)`
- **Header**: `max-width: 1440px` inner row, full-viewport-width bleed via `width: 100vw; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%)`
- **Footer**: Same full-bleed pattern, `max-width: 1126px` inner content
- **Static pages**: `width: 90%; max-width: 1600px; padding: 0 5%`

## Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Value | Effect |
|------------|-------|--------|
| Desktop → Tablet | `1024px` | Font sizes reduce, grid changes, padding adjusts |
| Tablet → Mobile | `900px` | Utility bar hides, tools nav shows |
| Small Tablet | `800px` | Product detail stacks to 1 column |
| Mobile | `700px` | Static pages collapse, footer nav collapses |
| Small Mobile | `600px` | Browse label hides, cart label hides |
| Extra Small | `480px` | Product grid goes 1 column |

## Rules

- **Never use hardcoded hex/rgb/hsl color values** for new code; use the named tokens above or CSS variables.
- **Spacing values must come from the spacing scale.** Avoid magic numbers like `13px` or `7px`.
- **Font sizes must come from the type scale.** Do not introduce new one-off sizes.
- **Buttons** must follow one of the three button patterns; do not create ad-hoc button styles.
- **Cards** must follow either the Product Card or Static Card pattern.
- **Eyebrow text** (uppercase labels above titles) always uses `font-size: 14px`, `font-weight: 700`, `text-transform: uppercase`, `letter-spacing: 0.56px`, and `color: rgb(0, 93, 171)`.
- **Full-bleed sections** (header, footer) use the `width: 100vw; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%)` pattern.
- **Media queries** must use the documented breakpoints; do not introduce custom breakpoints.
- **Dark mode** is handled exclusively via the CSS variables in the `@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark)` block; do not hardcode dark-mode-specific colors elsewhere.
